      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example retains its crisp throttle response and linear power delivery through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been serviced to maintain optimal cam timing. Riding on a refined MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, it offers the quintessential analog feedback enthusiasts crave. While showing honest signs of use, the mechanical vitals remain robust, making it a perfect candidate for the curves.",
